      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is the perfect opportunity for someone looking to put in some elbow grease and bring a car back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical attention and some cosmetic TLC, it remains a fantastic, budget-friendly entry point for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a rewarding restoration project. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
