    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty\u2014it is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in total mint condition. Not a scratch or a dent in sight, and the interior is so clean it still has that fresh new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you're going to love it as much as I have! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
